track_notes: This a nice way to reach the summit. As there are stone on the path you need some good shoes. The sloop is a bit hard at the beginning and goes soft later. You must go into the Fort to reach the summit.
track_title: Not the easiest, not the shortest

track_notes: About 30mn to reach the summit via this path. You will avoid the people on the road, and found the best place for the sight! Plenty room for the car.
Nice walk; starting from Nice (Aire St Michel) park along the small road. Get some water in summertime; on summit try to avoid crowded part, better to go on the back of the Fort (north part).
Walking around le mont chauve from the large car park! on the North face of the fort there is a large place for antenna

track_title: Climb by road, return by single.
